data.description: BACK ON Market! MOVE IN READY!  Co-op electric, bill was never more than $75:00   What you’ve worked for your whole life is waiting for you in sunny Florida. Surrounding area has  over 75,000 acres of chain lakes in Lake County. This beautiful home is the perfect place for  you to retire, in a well maintained gated 55+ community. Home is in excellent condition with newer  roof, HVAC heat pump, hot water heater (2022), newly remodeled kitchen with stainless  appliances, newly remodeled baths, all fixtures, and lighting. You will love this gorgeous split  floor plan with 3-bedrooms, 2-baths, high ceilings, new flooring, plantation shutters throughout  (2022), new vertical blind in great room (2023), new gutters (2022), new leaf guards (2023) with  transferrable warranty, enclosed patio, partially floored attic for storage, and sprinkler system. A  nature lover’s community, with miles of trails for you to enjoy strolling in your golf cart. Spend  your time in your own tropical paradise, or enjoying an active lifestyle for the fun in the sun  enthusiast on two beautiful championship golf courses, or in one of the three crystal clear pools.  Other amenities include three staffed activity centers offering over 100 activities, two fitness  centers, tennis, pickle ball, shuffleboard, bocce, volleyball, softball, fishing, and woodworking  shop. Also multiple events throughout the year like Music, Dances, and Trips. Orlando Disney  theme parks and MCO Airport within 45 minutes, Hard Rock Casino in Tampa 60 minutes,  Beaches are within an hour in a half, and Lake Ridge Winery and Vineyards 20 minutes  away. Seller is offering his inspection report and survey, for additional savings.
